optimising them wastes computation without benefit.

The score is computed in the same geometric space used by the C++ joint
pipeline (\code{unmix_autospectral_joint_cpp}):
\enumerate{
\item For each fluorophore \code{fl}, the pseudoinverse \code{U_nof} of the remaining
